# Alembic Migration Prosedürü

## Step 1: Spec

`Docs/02_DATABASE_SCHEMA.md` — tablo/kolon/index/enum tanımı önce docs'ta.

## Step 2: Model

`packages/shared/models/{entity}.py` — SQLAlchemy model, relationship, enum.

## Step 3: Revision

```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add_{table}_table"
```

Manuel review: drop table/data loss yok; `upgrade`/`downgrade` simetrik.

## Step 4: pgvector / Schema

Domain schema (`news`, `market`) için `op.execute('CREATE SCHEMA IF NOT EXISTS news')` migration'da.

## Step 5: Seed (opsiyonel)

`fixtures/` veya seed script — production verisi kullanma.

## Step 6: Test

`tests/integration/db/` — migration apply + model CRUD.

## Step 7: Docs

- [ ] `Docs/02_DATABASE_SCHEMA.md` güncellendi
- [ ] Production migration → kullanıcı onayı (`Docs/09` §6.1, §8.2)

